decks.notes: The main focus of this aggressive deck is to deploy fast and efficient threats on the battlefield to overwhelm the opponent quickly. The deck includes a mix of low-cost creatures with haste, like Goblin Guide and Monastery Swiftspear, along with burn spells such as Lightning Bolt and Lava Spike to deal direct damage to the opponent. The inclusion of cards like Tajic, Legion's Edge and Hero of Oxid Ridge provide additional sources of damage and resilience to removal spells. The deck aims to maintain pressure on the opponent while disrupting their game plan with cards like Mana Tithe and Path to Exile. Overall, the strategy revolves around a proactive playstyle, aiming to close out the game as quickly as possible.
